  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The family run Hotel Lanz welcome you to enjoy this lovely hotel with superb <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italian</a> food. The quiet location of the hotel is welcome by many and with the lifts and resort centre less than 300 metres away, it's the ideal base for your next ski holiday in an amazing ski area. Enjoy the relaxing facilities in the small spa including the sauna and Turkey bath or head to the bar and enjoy a drink or two with friends and family.</p>]]></listingDescription>
